Eviscerate - attack skill
------------------------------------------------------------
Eviscerate represents the blademaster swashbuckler's ability
to swiftly strike a decisive blow. It deals hideous damage
to the enemy--the stronger the enemy,the more damage it does.
An eviscerating attack is usually used to finish off an
already seriously wounded opponent, and should the attack
fail to slay the enemy, the swashbuckler will find himself
off-balance and disadvantaged in combat. Naturally, such a
bold move cannot be repeated even on the densest of enemies.

GL: 14
SP: variable (60-300)
command:  eviscerate <target> (defaults to opponent if in combat)
duration: instant
